Project Dependency Graph

Dependency Tree

  • net.automatalib:automata-util:jar:0.3.1-ase2013-tutorial-r1
    AutomataLib :: Utilities

    Description: This artifact provides various common utility operations for analyzing and manipulating automata and graphs, such as traversal, minimization and copying.

    URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/automata-util/

    Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007

    • net.automatalib:automata-commons-util:jar:0.3.1-ase2013-tutorial-r1 (compile)
      AutomataLib :: Commons :: Utilities

      Description: Basic utility library containing several useful classes (e.g., a Pair class) to ease everyday programming.

      URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/automata-commons-parent/automata-commons-util/

      Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007

      • com.google.guava:guava:jar:15.0 (compile)
        Guava: Google Core Libraries for Java

        Description: Guava is a suite of core and expanded libraries that include utility classes, google's collections, io classes, and much much more. Guava has two code dependencies - javax.annotation per the JSR-305 spec and javax.inject per the JSR-330 spec.

        URL: http://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries/guava

        Project License: The Apache Software License, Version 2.0

    • net.automatalib:automata-commons-smartcollections:jar:0.3.1-ase2013-tutorial-r1 (compile)
      AutomataLib :: Commons :: Smart Collections

      Description: This library provides efficient implementations for various collection data structures (esp. linked lists and priority queues), which have very insufficient implementation in the Java Collections Foundations that makes it hard or even impossible to exploit their efficiencies.

      URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/automata-commons-parent/automata-commons-smartcollections/

      Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007

    • net.automatalib:automata-api:jar:0.3.1-ase2013-tutorial-r1 (compile)
      AutomataLib :: API

      Description: This artifact contains the API of AutomataLib, which mainly consists of interfaces for the various concepts and automaton models supported by the AutomataLib core. In addition to that, it also defines some fundamental classes for dealing with words of symbols.

      URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/automata-api/

      Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007

    • net.automatalib:automata-core:jar:0.3.1-ase2013-tutorial-r1 (compile)
      AutomataLib :: Core

      Description: The core artifact of AutomataLib. This library contains concrete implementations for many of the automaton model interfaces defined in the API artifact, as well as abstract base classes that facilitate implementing new automaton model classes. Note that concrete algorithms (traversal, reachability analysis etc.) are not in the scope of this artifact.

      URL: http://misberner.github.io/automatalib/maven-site/automata-core/

      Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 29 June 2007
